WEBVTT

00:00.024 --> 00:04.972
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:05.944 --> 00:08.652
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.784 --> 00:13.792
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.816 --> 00:18.572
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.608 --> 00:22.636
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.640 --> 00:27.584
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.608 --> 00:30.880
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:30.904 --> 00:34.368
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.392 --> 00:39.640
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.640 --> 00:41.258
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.258 --> 00:44.736
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.760 --> 00:48.032
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.056 --> 00:53.728
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.752 --> 00:55.096
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.096 --> 00:58.432
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.456 --> 01:01.804
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:01.912 --> 01:07.109
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.109 --> 01:08.792
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.792 --> 01:12.192
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.216 --> 01:15.616
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.640 --> 01:21.216
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.240 --> 01:24.652
♪ I love you ♪

01:26.930 --> 01:27.720
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.720 --> 01:30.664
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 4=

01:30.664 --> 01:34.304
(Hello, Sheng. I'm Qiang Qingci.)

01:52.732 --> 01:54.392
Did you check Weibo?

01:55.611 --> 01:57.491
Tell you what, I was almost in tears.

01:57.491 --> 02:00.091
Do you know that my favorite
posted 20 minutes ago

02:00.091 --> 02:02.912
on Weibo about his favorite voice?

02:03.452 --> 02:05.711
I was so touched.

02:06.412 --> 02:07.651
I'm at work right now.

02:07.651 --> 02:09.952
Let's talk
when we get home tonight, okay?

02:13.651 --> 02:16.352
(It's not so coincidental, right?)

02:18.252 --> 02:21.692
Yiru, have you eaten?

02:21.692 --> 02:23.811
I haven't,
but I'll get off work with you

02:23.811 --> 02:25.311
when your dad comes.

02:31.404 --> 02:34.364
(Wangjia Supermarket)

02:57.252 --> 03:00.991
Sheng, do you have
a favorite dubbing actor?

03:04.732 --> 03:08.132
I haven't really delved into it.

03:08.132 --> 03:09.831
I guess they all sound pretty good.

03:10.452 --> 03:14.292
There are actually a lot of good voices
on the internet.

03:14.292 --> 03:16.452
For example, in some of our TV shows,

03:16.452 --> 03:19.692
the actor might be the one talking,
but the voice may be not theirs.

03:19.692 --> 03:21.672
It could be dubbed by a dubbing actor.

03:22.572 --> 03:23.931
I know.

03:23.931 --> 03:25.931
And there are a lot of radio dramas,

03:25.931 --> 03:27.931
in which voice actors gather
to voice their favorite novels

03:27.931 --> 03:30.192
for sharing the same interest.

03:31.692 --> 03:33.072
I see.

03:37.426 --> 03:38.569
(Voicemail, Moqingcheng)

03:38.569 --> 03:39.991
(Qiang Qingci?)

03:47.172 --> 03:48.732
(It's not that I don't want
to listen to it, )

03:48.732 --> 03:51.151
(but your fan is right next to me.)

03:54.651 --> 03:56.132
I know you're at work,

03:56.132 --> 03:58.771
but I think something big has happened.

03:58.771 --> 03:59.692
You know what?

03:59.692 --> 04:01.931
Qiang Qingci shared our song
ten minutes ago.

04:01.931 --> 04:03.012
I mean the one we made

04:03.012 --> 04:05.692
ten days ago to celebrate
the 16th anniversary of his debut.

04:05.692 --> 04:06.711
I...

04:08.612 --> 04:11.851
Sorry, I played it on speaker.

04:11.851 --> 04:15.411
(Wangjia Supermarket)
It's okay. No customer anyway. Go ahead.

04:15.411 --> 04:17.471
Thank you.

04:19.812 --> 04:21.052
Let me catch my breath.

04:21.052 --> 04:23.492
I'm going to tell you
another devastating news.

04:23.492 --> 04:25.372
You know, when he shared our song,

04:25.372 --> 04:27.411
we wished him
to be out of bachelorhood soon.

04:27.411 --> 04:29.291
And he said... Wait.

04:29.291 --> 04:30.411
Let me catch my breath again.

04:30.411 --> 04:32.492
He replied with one simple sentence,

04:32.492 --> 04:33.892
"Thank you, I'm trying".

04:33.892 --> 04:35.816
Listen, it's not "I will try".

04:35.816 --> 04:38.071
It's "I'm trying",
in present continuous tense!

04:38.071 --> 04:40.311
I'll wager a truckload of cucumbers.
It's definitely Shengshengman.

04:40.311 --> 04:44.711
I... I'll raise the bet.
It must be Shengshengman.

04:46.411 --> 04:48.151
- Welcome.
- Welcome.

05:02.012 --> 05:05.091
(Gu Sheng, stay calm.
He is Qiang Qingci after all.)

05:05.091 --> 05:07.171
(He hasn't really said anything.)

05:07.171 --> 05:10.392
(Besides, even if he has,
it has nothing to do with you.)

05:15.531 --> 05:18.091
(No, I can't stay calm at all.)

05:18.091 --> 05:21.052
(It's not good to have too much contact
with someone who has a halo.)

05:21.052 --> 05:23.072
(It's too easy to let my mind wander.)

05:29.772 --> 05:33.244
(Wangjia Supermarket)

05:40.211 --> 05:41.971
Thank you.

05:41.971 --> 05:44.052
One of you can get off work,
and the other can go home for dinner.

05:44.052 --> 05:45.591
- Thanks, dad.
- Thanks, boss.

05:48.531 --> 05:51.651
Dong, how was your day?
Have you gotten used to it?

05:51.651 --> 05:53.052
It's pretty good.

05:53.052 --> 05:54.392
Thanks, boss.

05:56.372 --> 06:00.028
I just finished a busy period.
I might sleep until midnight.

06:00.731 --> 06:03.091
Just leave a message
if you need something.

06:03.091 --> 06:04.671
I'll see it when I wake up.

06:05.812 --> 06:06.851
Goodbye, boss.

06:06.851 --> 06:07.911
Goodbye.

06:09.211 --> 06:12.531
Sheng, you haven't left yet.
Aren't you hungry?

06:12.531 --> 06:14.052
I'm leaving now.

06:14.052 --> 06:15.388
Okay.

06:17.091 --> 06:21.372
I can't find my keys.
Where are my bike keys?

06:21.372 --> 06:22.731
I know. Let me get them for you.

06:22.731 --> 06:23.240
You don't have to.

06:23.240 --> 06:24.544
Just stay here.

06:26.572 --> 06:27.171
What's wrong?

06:27.171 --> 06:27.971
She forgot her keys.

06:27.971 --> 06:28.651
Bye, boss.

06:28.651 --> 06:29.831
See you.

06:31.171 --> 06:34.132
Look, here they are.
You must have forgotten them.

06:34.132 --> 06:34.651
Thank you.

06:34.651 --> 06:38.844
You're welcome.
Sheng, your face is red. Are you okay?

06:39.531 --> 06:40.732
Really?

06:42.612 --> 06:43.771
My dad is really not frugal.

06:43.771 --> 06:46.411
He turns the AC so high.
It's making me hot.

06:46.411 --> 06:48.331
Alright then, I'm leaving now. Goodbye.

06:48.331 --> 06:48.932
Goodbye.

06:48.932 --> 06:50.076
Goodbye.

06:54.331 --> 06:55.971
Call me when you get home.

06:55.971 --> 06:57.452
(Happy New Year)
Okay, just go back.

06:57.452 --> 06:58.752
Okay.

07:11.340 --> 07:13.692
(Performing audio export)

07:15.331 --> 07:16.471
Perfect.

07:34.771 --> 07:36.552
It's already 11 o'clock.

07:38.291 --> 07:39.552
(I woke up.)

07:44.771 --> 07:47.632
(Didn't he say
he's going to sleep till 1 a.m.?)

07:51.452 --> 07:53.171
(It's hard to stay up late, isn't it?)

07:53.171 --> 07:55.632
(Do you want to drink some water
and go back to sleep?)

07:58.052 --> 07:59.432
(I'm reading emails.)

08:03.731 --> 08:07.151
(That means he's busy?)

08:09.731 --> 08:10.911
(Are you busy?)

08:12.851 --> 08:15.911
(I just have finished a song
and have some free time.)

08:18.012 --> 08:20.271
(What is it? Did you write it?)

08:21.571 --> 08:25.031
(Whether It's Dawn or Dusk
in a young master's voice.)

08:40.411 --> 08:44.171
The water fairy is about to leave
by riding a carp.

08:44.171 --> 08:48.092
The spring night retreats
in teary redness.

08:48.092 --> 08:51.811
Whether it's dawn or dusk,

08:51.811 --> 08:55.232
even ten cups of fine wine
fail to intoxicate.

08:55.972 --> 08:59.451
When will the trifles of love end?

08:59.451 --> 09:03.632
Sobriety announces
the conferring of a peerage.

09:07.051 --> 09:09.291
(You are really too good at picking.)

09:09.291 --> 09:12.632
(The nest lines of the song
are all here.)

09:15.372 --> 09:16.911
Exactly this song.

09:18.492 --> 09:22.472
The lyrics are quite interesting.
I just found them.

09:37.252 --> 09:40.232
(Next time, don't stay so late.
It's very damaging to your voice.)

09:41.411 --> 09:44.776
(Go get some sesame oil in the kitchen,
and take a small sip.)

09:44.776 --> 09:46.551
(You'll feel better tomorrow morning.)

09:49.132 --> 09:50.712
(Will it work?)

09:59.171 --> 10:00.671
Sesame oil...

10:15.852 --> 10:18.512
(Better indeed.)

10:42.691 --> 10:44.191
(I've had some.)

10:45.892 --> 10:48.872
(Typing is a bit tiresome.
Can we have voice chat?)

11:02.972 --> 11:04.071
(OK.)

11:04.936 --> 11:06.944
(Moqingcheng has invited you
to a voice call)

11:08.651 --> 11:09.852
Hello?

11:10.612 --> 11:11.712
I'm listening.

11:12.852 --> 11:14.271
You may go on then.

11:15.492 --> 11:17.151
(Go on? With what?)

11:19.612 --> 11:22.571
I just went to drink some sesame oil.

11:22.571 --> 11:24.571
Aren't you sleepy now?

11:24.571 --> 11:28.352
I just woke up,
thinking of finding something to eat.

11:30.051 --> 11:32.191
(Silence is even more awkward.)

11:35.691 --> 11:40.512
I just went to the kitchen
and saw the conch meat my mom prepared.

11:41.064 --> 11:41.612
Really?

11:41.612 --> 11:45.171
Tomorrow noon,
we might eat scalded conch meat slices.

11:45.171 --> 11:47.311
Actually, I quite like it.

11:48.492 --> 11:50.232
I will check the recipe.

11:55.771 --> 11:56.872
You are awake.

11:57.228 --> 11:58.396
(Sheng)

11:59.492 --> 12:00.732
How much longer do you guys need?

12:00.732 --> 12:03.291
About an hour. We're almost done.

12:03.291 --> 12:04.691
By the way, don't leave.

12:04.691 --> 12:06.892
Once they're done recording,
I'll record your parts.

12:06.892 --> 12:08.972
After finishing recording,
we can go out and eat something.

12:08.972 --> 12:10.071
Okay.

12:16.531 --> 12:18.352
I'll start reading.

12:22.332 --> 12:27.492
Cut the conch meat into large slices,
and rinse them clean with warm water.

12:27.492 --> 12:30.451
Blanch the flowering cabbages
and mushroom with boiling water.

12:30.451 --> 12:34.771
Mix chopped spring onions and ginger
with rice wine and water to get juice.

12:34.771 --> 12:36.712
Then mince the chicken meat

12:36.712 --> 12:40.012
and knead it into balls
with a diameter of about one centimeter.

12:40.012 --> 12:44.051
Then scald the conch slices
and chicken meat balls in boiling water.

12:44.051 --> 12:47.071
Finally,
pour everything hot into the soup bowl.

12:48.531 --> 12:50.031
It will be ready to eat.

12:51.931 --> 12:54.712
I know
it's a famous dish in Shandong cuisine.

12:58.892 --> 13:00.431
I seem even hungrier now.

13:03.051 --> 13:06.092
I was wrong.
I shouldn't talk about food at night.

13:06.092 --> 13:07.271
It's okay.

13:09.571 --> 13:11.012
It's getting a bit late now.

13:11.012 --> 13:13.352
Are you going to sleep?

13:14.651 --> 13:16.291
Almost.

13:16.291 --> 13:19.451
Then rest early. Good night.

13:19.451 --> 13:20.712
Good night.

13:30.852 --> 13:32.151
Good night.

13:50.651 --> 13:51.892
What are you doing?

13:51.892 --> 13:53.492
Ordering takeout for everyone.

13:54.771 --> 13:57.051
I heard you booked a recording studio.

13:57.051 --> 13:58.872
Are you going to meet Shengshengman?

14:00.291 --> 14:02.112
It's for work.

14:02.811 --> 14:04.112
Mr. Mo.

14:04.612 --> 14:05.911
Are you...

14:07.092 --> 14:10.811
He's the new intern, Xiyou,
responsible for the receptionist work.

14:10.811 --> 14:15.012
If you need to print documents
or order takeout, just ask him.

14:15.012 --> 14:16.191
Hello, Mr. Mo.

14:17.051 --> 14:18.411
Hello, Xiyou.

14:18.411 --> 14:22.311
Mr. Mo, do you have an online name?

14:22.852 --> 14:25.132
No sharing of work photos.

14:25.132 --> 14:27.252
No sharing of employee information.

14:27.252 --> 14:28.531
Didn't Doudou tell you?

14:28.531 --> 14:32.092
She did. And I signed a contract
that includes a NDA.

14:32.092 --> 14:36.712
So Mr. Mo, are you really Qiang Qingci?

14:40.212 --> 14:41.771
Yes, I am.

14:41.771 --> 14:42.291
M...

14:42.291 --> 14:44.531
Find out
what everyone wants to eat for me.

14:44.531 --> 14:47.012
I'm treating tonight. Thank you.

14:47.012 --> 14:49.232
Sure, you're welcome.

14:51.372 --> 14:54.892
M-Mao...

14:54.892 --> 14:57.651
Enough. I know you're excited.

14:57.651 --> 15:00.051
Mao, I've been his fan for many years.

15:00.051 --> 15:01.771
It's not because he's famous,

15:01.771 --> 15:02.931
but that I really like his work.

15:02.931 --> 15:05.012
Understood. Listen.

15:05.012 --> 15:07.051
If you learn voice acting well
at Perfect Voice,

15:07.051 --> 15:10.852
you'll witness the birth
of more of his outstanding works.

15:10.852 --> 15:11.811
Okay, Mao.

15:11.811 --> 15:13.132
Young man!

15:13.132 --> 15:15.852
Mao, what do you want to eat tonight?
I'll order for you.

15:15.852 --> 15:17.116
Don't get too excited.

15:26.132 --> 15:29.171
(Weibo post of Xiyou)
(My first day as an intern in the recording studio.)

15:29.171 --> 15:32.372
(And I actually saw my idol,
Qiang Qingci.)

15:32.372 --> 15:34.411
(Idol, please rest assured.
As I promised, )

15:34.411 --> 15:37.531
(I will never
leak any of your photos or information.)

15:37.531 --> 15:39.771
(But, can I just be honest?)

15:39.771 --> 15:42.051
(Idol, you truly are so handsome.)

15:42.051 --> 15:44.671
(Lucky you, Shengshengman.)

15:46.651 --> 15:50.712
Aren't you curious about
what Qiang Qingci looks like?

15:53.972 --> 15:57.051
Actually, it's alright.

15:57.051 --> 16:01.671
'Alright'?
He's been your idol for so many years.

16:04.571 --> 16:08.571
Many people online know each other
for years without meeting face to face.

16:08.571 --> 16:09.872
It's quite normal.

16:10.771 --> 16:12.112
Keep concealing.

16:12.612 --> 16:14.311
I'm not concealing.

16:16.291 --> 16:21.191
Aren't you the least bit
curious about his looks?

16:22.571 --> 16:26.271
No. I'm going to play piano for a while.

16:45.771 --> 16:49.651
I'm going to our studio to record a song
in a couple of days.

16:49.651 --> 16:51.708
What song are you recording
on a major holiday?

16:52.332 --> 16:55.171
It's the pre-release
in collaboration with the Perfect Voice.

16:55.171 --> 16:57.052
I promised them during the New Year.

16:57.052 --> 16:59.332
I recorded a demo during these days
and gave it to them.

16:59.332 --> 17:01.171
Seems they're not quite satisfied
with it on their side.

17:01.171 --> 17:02.632
We've discussed
about doing a re-recording.

17:02.632 --> 17:04.532
Our studio just got prepared,

17:04.532 --> 17:07.171
so the effect might be better
if we record there.

17:07.171 --> 17:09.832
No problem. I'll give you the door card.
You can go anytime.

17:10.971 --> 17:13.491
But our studio
hires freelance sound engineers.

17:13.491 --> 17:16.252
During such a major holiday,
there may be no one available for you.

17:16.772 --> 17:18.231
Well...

17:23.372 --> 17:25.020
(Voicemail from Moqingcheng)

17:30.491 --> 17:32.592
How did
the scalded conch meat slices taste?

17:38.532 --> 17:43.471
(Oh, my God. Gu Sheng, )
are you fantasizing about him?

17:44.572 --> 17:46.451
(No, no, no.)

17:46.451 --> 17:49.892
(It must be the rumors
that gave me the psychological hint.)

17:49.892 --> 17:52.632
(He has no feelings for me.
Absolutely no feelings.)

17:53.171 --> 17:57.052
(I must not over-interpret things.
Wake up. Wake up.)

17:57.052 --> 17:59.911
(Don't take everything
on the internet seriously.)

18:04.451 --> 18:05.872
(It's quite tasty.)

18:14.251 --> 18:16.072
(Have you eaten?)

18:21.411 --> 18:23.352
(I'm having a boxed lunch.)

18:25.332 --> 18:26.632
(Are you not at home?)

18:29.211 --> 18:32.751
(Didn't somebody mention you in Weibo,
saying they saw me at the studio?)

18:42.451 --> 18:44.552
(I haven't gotten around
to checking Weibo.)

18:48.011 --> 18:52.272
I heard you weren't very satisfied
with the demo.

19:01.171 --> 19:05.112
If it could be recorded in the studio,
the effect would be much better.

19:08.211 --> 19:10.671
But the current effect
is almost all right.

19:11.171 --> 19:14.812
I've scheduled the recording time
for this song with the planner

19:15.200 --> 19:16.764
and booked the recording studio.

19:18.612 --> 19:20.604
That's great if you have...

19:21.211 --> 19:24.352
(He scheduled a time
and booked the studio?)

19:25.411 --> 19:28.352
(He means he wants to record with me?)

19:32.092 --> 19:33.151
What's wrong?

19:34.532 --> 19:35.951
Nothing.

19:38.772 --> 19:42.711
(He means he wants to meet me.)

19:51.931 --> 19:54.151
It's temporarily set for Sunday
at 3:00 p.m.

19:55.372 --> 19:56.592
See you on Sunday.

20:00.931 --> 20:02.552
See you on Sunday.

20:03.560 --> 20:06.011
Who are you going to see on Sunday?
What demo are you going to record?

20:06.011 --> 20:07.431
Do I know him?

20:08.651 --> 20:12.251
Nothing. A friend wants me
to help him record a song.

20:12.251 --> 20:13.911
Friend? What friend?

20:15.052 --> 20:17.872
It's someone you don't know.
I'll continue to play.

20:37.452 --> 20:44.156
(Theory of Harmony)

20:45.996 --> 20:47.932
(Tianzi No. 1 Recording Studio)

20:52.012 --> 20:53.504
(Tianzi No. 1 Recording Studio)

21:08.812 --> 21:13.231
Building number six. Where is it?

21:14.188 --> 21:15.868
(Beautiful Mood)

21:21.260 --> 21:23.100
(The Perfect Voice Studio)

21:40.092 --> 21:43.951
(It's only 2:30.
The appointment is at 3:00.)

21:45.171 --> 21:47.951
It's impolite to go up so early, right?

22:05.132 --> 22:07.468
(The Perfect Voice Studio)

22:07.468 --> 22:10.908
(Tianzi No. 1 Recording Studio)

22:21.251 --> 22:22.812
Hello, please come in.

22:22.812 --> 22:24.151
Hello.

22:25.036 --> 22:26.971
(The Perfect Voice Studio)

22:26.971 --> 22:28.872
You're here to record, right?

22:29.772 --> 22:30.572
Yes.

22:30.572 --> 22:33.392
All the rooms are full.
What time is your appointment?

22:34.052 --> 22:35.312
3:00.

22:38.011 --> 22:39.792
3:00?

22:41.251 --> 22:43.032
Are you a friend of Mo Qingcheng?

22:45.491 --> 22:47.532
It's Qiang...

22:47.532 --> 22:48.671
Yes, that's right.

22:50.052 --> 22:52.032
This way. The very last room over there.

23:15.491 --> 23:16.511
Hello.

23:18.011 --> 23:19.312
Hello.

23:23.404 --> 23:26.620
(Control Room)

23:41.532 --> 23:43.852
Shengshengman? Hello.

23:43.852 --> 23:46.592
I am Qiang Qingci.

23:48.812 --> 23:50.940
Sorry for the joke. I'm Juemei.

23:51.491 --> 23:53.892
I will call them. Wait a moment.

23:53.892 --> 23:55.671
Shengshengman is here.

23:57.171 --> 23:58.892
Hello, hello. I...

23:58.892 --> 23:59.011
Hi.

23:59.011 --> 24:01.372
I-I-I am Feishao.

24:01.372 --> 24:06.032
I was eating hot pot next to you
when you two were snuggling.

24:07.852 --> 24:10.288
That's enough. Doudou.

24:10.312 --> 24:12.132
(Recording room)
Don't scare her.

24:12.132 --> 24:14.332
Shengshengman, I didn't...
Shengshengman, did I scare you?

24:14.332 --> 24:15.171
No.

24:15.171 --> 24:17.572
Look at you people.
Make way, make way.

24:17.572 --> 24:19.612
Qiang Qingci won't come
because something came up.

24:19.612 --> 24:20.532
You are scaring her.

24:20.532 --> 24:21.671
Exactly.

24:22.411 --> 24:24.411
Shengshengman, right?

24:24.411 --> 24:26.011
Give me the things and have a seat.

24:26.011 --> 24:27.491
There is no need. Thank you.

24:27.491 --> 24:29.812
Then I will prepare.
Give me some time, okay?

24:29.812 --> 24:30.892
Okay.

24:30.892 --> 24:32.332
You don't have to bring these things.

24:32.332 --> 24:34.312
We've finally met.

24:35.656 --> 24:36.700
Your backpack.

24:37.251 --> 24:38.352
Okay.

24:39.132 --> 24:40.372
It's a bit heavy.

24:40.372 --> 24:42.251
What's with the backpack?

24:42.251 --> 24:46.011
I am Doudoubing.

24:46.011 --> 24:50.431
Hello. Actually, I know you guys.

24:51.011 --> 24:52.211
We've talked online before.

24:52.211 --> 24:53.852
Yes, I know.

24:53.852 --> 24:56.892
I didn't expect you to be so beautiful.

24:56.892 --> 24:59.671
I just didn't dare to talk to you
if I were a boy.

25:01.052 --> 25:03.292
Is Mr. Qiang Qingci not coming today?

25:03.292 --> 25:04.731
He has something urgent to deal with.

25:04.731 --> 25:07.132
He's busier than any of us.

25:07.132 --> 25:10.572
But don't worry. He's entrusted me
to take good care of you

25:10.572 --> 25:12.411
and not let these guys scare you.

25:12.411 --> 25:13.251
She means you.

25:13.251 --> 25:14.372
We didn't scare anyone.

25:14.372 --> 25:15.491
- Who...
- Scaring people

25:15.491 --> 25:16.211
is what you do?

25:16.211 --> 25:17.852
I heard the lead actress is here.

25:17.852 --> 25:19.931
I can't even happily sleep knowing this.

25:19.931 --> 25:22.431
Let me introduce myself. I'm Wang Ke.

25:23.772 --> 25:25.171
Hello.

25:25.171 --> 25:27.211
We were talking about
not getting scared by you guys.

25:27.211 --> 25:29.011
Please don't mind.
We've known each other for years.

25:29.011 --> 25:30.471
We just like to joke around.

25:31.092 --> 25:32.852
It's completely okay.

25:32.852 --> 25:34.231
Yeah, joking around.

25:34.812 --> 25:36.491
Pour a glass of water.

25:36.491 --> 25:37.691
She's right. Just go.

25:37.691 --> 25:39.372
You, go pour a glass of water. Quickly.

25:39.372 --> 25:40.671
Okay.

25:41.171 --> 25:42.332
I'll do it.

25:42.332 --> 25:43.868
Look at Xiyou.

25:44.424 --> 25:46.951
Look at how proactive he is.

25:52.251 --> 25:54.092
You will have to record later.

25:54.092 --> 25:56.171
So I poured some warm water for you.

25:56.171 --> 25:56.971
Thank you.

25:56.971 --> 25:58.431
Considerate, huh?

26:04.772 --> 26:06.151
Drink it.

26:07.931 --> 26:11.431
I have to go back to school in a bit.

26:13.011 --> 26:15.292
Then let's hurry up
and get down to business, okay?

26:15.292 --> 26:16.211
Yeah. Right. Let's do it.

26:16.211 --> 26:17.772
Or Shengshengman
will be late for going back.

26:17.772 --> 26:20.052
That's right. The lyrics
have been printed and placed inside.

26:20.052 --> 26:22.508
But you probably don't need them
since you've memorized them all, right?

26:22.612 --> 26:23.931
Since Mr. Mo can't make it back,

26:23.931 --> 26:27.332
it'll just be you, me, Wang Ke,
and Doudou, the four of us recording.

26:27.332 --> 26:29.612
Two people need to stay to
deliver the vocals and match the timing.

26:29.612 --> 26:31.372
She needs to go back to school.
Let her record first.

26:31.372 --> 26:32.052
Okay.

26:32.052 --> 26:33.532
It's okay for me anyway.

26:33.532 --> 26:35.251
- It's fine.
- You go first.

26:35.251 --> 26:36.852
We'll be here all the time.
There's no rush.

26:36.852 --> 26:38.731
- Right. Come on.
- Let's go.

26:38.731 --> 26:39.804
Let's go.

26:40.532 --> 26:42.411
So Sheng records first, right?

26:42.411 --> 26:43.892
I'll adjust the microphone for you.

26:43.892 --> 26:45.411
Give me the backpack.

26:45.411 --> 26:46.211
Thank you.

26:46.211 --> 26:47.388
Go ahead.

27:33.651 --> 27:35.312
Can you hear me?

27:36.532 --> 27:37.651
Yes.

27:37.651 --> 27:40.832
You are too close to the microphone.
Can you move back a bit?

27:43.092 --> 27:45.092
- That's right.
- She's a bit nervous.

27:45.092 --> 27:47.151
Alright.
If you are ready, let's get started.

28:05.411 --> 28:06.821
(The Perfect Voice Studio)
As far as I know,

28:06.821 --> 28:08.132
Shengshengman is definitely not simple.

28:08.132 --> 28:09.872
- Right.
- She and Mr. Mo...

28:11.892 --> 28:13.352
Mr. Mo.

28:14.380 --> 28:16.508
(The Perfect Voice Studio)

28:17.292 --> 28:18.872
She's here.

28:20.012 --> 28:22.332
(The Perfect Voice Studio)

28:33.011 --> 28:34.552
Has he entered?

28:35.451 --> 28:36.872
Has he?

28:39.211 --> 28:42.892
♪ Blending into the bustling street,
turning back with a glance ♪

28:42.892 --> 28:45.892
♪ The prosperous world is in my eyes ♪

28:45.892 --> 28:52.532
♪ I travel around,
freely living to my heart's content ♪

28:52.532 --> 28:53.251
Why are you back?

28:53.251 --> 28:54.092
Won't you be busy?

28:54.092 --> 28:55.491
♪ A name renowned through the ages ♪

28:55.491 --> 28:56.976
You came to substitute me?

28:57.000 --> 28:58.032
She's inside.

29:00.132 --> 29:07.451
♪ Roaming the world,
fearless of love or hatred ♪

29:07.451 --> 29:08.751
♪ Joy or sorrow ♪

29:46.132 --> 29:47.411
Not bad.

29:47.411 --> 29:48.931
Okay.

29:48.931 --> 29:52.231
Mo Qingcheng,
you have eternal yogurt addiction, huh?

30:06.924 --> 30:11.580
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

30:12.524 --> 30:15.356
♪ My heart is racing ♪

30:16.648 --> 30:20.476
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

30:21.332 --> 30:22.671
Hello, Sheng.

30:23.772 --> 30:25.272
I'm Qiang Qingci.

30:26.316 --> 30:29.148
♪ What kind of look ♪

30:32.211 --> 30:33.471
Hello.

30:34.088 --> 30:37.980
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

30:38.612 --> 30:42.671
(I didn't expect it to be him,
that doctor.)

30:46.440 --> 30:47.976
♪ I love you ♪

30:47.976 --> 30:50.888
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

30:50.888 --> 30:53.884
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

30:54.011 --> 30:58.612
Mao, could you please play
what you've just recorded for me again?

30:58.612 --> 31:00.072
This is the situation now.

31:00.691 --> 31:02.532
Everyone has had a turn at recording.

31:02.532 --> 31:04.691
Sheng has already done the second round.

31:04.691 --> 31:07.991
Are you listening to all theirs
or just hers?

31:09.491 --> 31:10.632
Everyone's.

31:13.011 --> 31:15.592
Sheng, come out and rest a bit.

31:17.171 --> 31:18.231
Okay.

31:20.651 --> 31:22.032
Here, Mr. Mo.

31:22.316 --> 31:27.304
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

31:27.304 --> 31:28.904
♪ I love you ♪

31:28.904 --> 31:32.520
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

31:32.520 --> 31:35.784
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

31:35.784 --> 31:41.256
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

31:41.256 --> 31:44.828
♪ I love you ♪

31:46.211 --> 31:49.431
What do you think?
Isn't he quite eye candy?

31:54.931 --> 31:56.312
He's pretty handsome.

32:16.852 --> 32:19.951
Are you wondering if we've met before?

32:21.332 --> 32:24.532
You two have met?
Why didn't you tell you earlier?

32:24.532 --> 32:25.691
Before Sheng arrived,

32:25.691 --> 32:28.171
we were planning on
where to take her out to eat tonight,

32:28.171 --> 32:31.491
and at the same time instill the image
of you being an unparalleled great man.

32:31.491 --> 32:32.572
You'd never get a turn at that.

32:32.572 --> 32:34.372
You have cut the corner.

32:34.372 --> 32:36.691
Look at us. We're all still in the dark.

32:36.691 --> 32:40.691
Is that a photo or a video, Mr. Mo?

32:40.691 --> 32:44.171
You haven't secretly
posted a video online, have you?

32:44.171 --> 32:45.731
The uncut and uncensored kind?

32:45.731 --> 32:48.792
Feishao, don't discuss taboo topics.

32:54.812 --> 32:56.191
We've met before.

32:57.052 --> 32:59.911
I'm just not sure if you remember.

33:01.011 --> 33:05.431
I do. You were walking a dog.

33:09.052 --> 33:12.431
I never thought it would be you.

33:13.572 --> 33:16.392
Likewise. I didn't expect it to be you.

33:17.372 --> 33:21.731
Wait. What are you guys talking about?
We don't quite understand.

33:21.731 --> 33:23.292
Wait. How did you guys meet?

33:23.292 --> 33:24.251
Exactly.

33:24.251 --> 33:26.852
How we met is between us.

33:26.852 --> 33:28.911
You don't have to jump in
and make a fuss.

33:29.768 --> 33:30.292
Alright.

33:30.292 --> 33:33.671
They met before
but saying it's the first time.

33:35.812 --> 33:38.272
I'll go record first. Let's talk later.

33:40.612 --> 33:41.812
Ask later.

33:41.812 --> 33:42.651
Why don't you ask?

33:42.651 --> 33:44.072
You ask.

33:55.892 --> 33:57.312
Just ask.

33:57.812 --> 33:59.692
Sheng, how did you...

33:59.692 --> 34:00.692
What are you two up to?

34:00.692 --> 34:02.571
Sheng, we shouldn't linger here.

34:02.571 --> 34:05.051
Let me take you to have a look around.

34:05.051 --> 34:06.051
Doudou.

34:06.051 --> 34:09.471
My favorite place is here, the pantry.

34:10.692 --> 34:12.172
Doudou.

34:12.172 --> 34:15.252
Here we have beverages,
fruits, and snacks.

34:15.252 --> 34:16.511
Help yourself.

34:18.571 --> 34:20.611
There's quite a variety
of things available here.

34:20.611 --> 34:22.931
You even have game machines
and the medical kit.

34:22.931 --> 34:24.931
They don't usually
take care of their health.

34:24.931 --> 34:26.332
I have to prepare everything.

34:26.332 --> 34:30.076
We have stomach medicine
and cold medicine inside. Sit down.

34:33.611 --> 34:35.531
Doudou, you are so thoughtful.

34:35.531 --> 34:39.252
It's mainly because we've worked together
for so many years.

34:39.252 --> 34:41.172
We're like a family now.

34:41.172 --> 34:43.451
I heard from Juemei
you're a senior this year.

34:43.451 --> 34:44.732
Did you find a job?

34:45.292 --> 34:46.531
I got accepted into graduate school.

34:46.531 --> 34:50.300
A top student, huh?
You and Mo Qingcheng are quite alike.

34:50.856 --> 34:52.212
Does he also have good grades?

34:52.212 --> 34:55.772
More than good. He basically advances
without having to take tests.

34:55.772 --> 34:57.511
So I said you two are alike.

34:58.611 --> 35:03.996
Sheng, where did you meet
Mo Qingcheng before?

35:07.531 --> 35:09.471
You can't say it
because it's a special place?

35:10.531 --> 35:11.892
He won't let you say it, right?

35:11.892 --> 35:15.611
No, it was just a coincidence.

35:15.611 --> 35:17.692
We met in the supermarket of my family.

35:17.692 --> 35:20.131
In the supermarket of your family?
Were you having a blind date there?

35:20.131 --> 35:21.971
No, it was a coincidence.

35:21.971 --> 35:26.011
A coincidence?
That's too much of a coincidence.

35:26.011 --> 35:29.232
I also find it incredible.

35:30.051 --> 35:32.261
Doudou, Mr. Mo said
he's finished recording.

35:32.261 --> 35:33.051
You can come in.

35:33.051 --> 35:37.152
So fast? He is getting quicker.

35:38.131 --> 35:39.471
Come. This way.

35:43.812 --> 35:45.011
Mao, play it again.

35:45.011 --> 35:45.252
Again?

35:45.252 --> 35:46.451
How is it?

35:46.451 --> 35:49.212
I have an iron flute of south

35:49.212 --> 35:51.652
that wants to lean
on a fragrant, snowy twig.

35:51.652 --> 35:53.931
Blowing through the jade dawn,

35:53.931 --> 35:56.471
its clear shadow is hard to catch

35:57.451 --> 36:00.931
in the fluff flying across the sky.

36:00.931 --> 36:01.451
This one is good.

36:01.451 --> 36:05.091
Drifting away, I and you
paddle on the cloud.

36:05.091 --> 36:06.372
Play it again, Mao.

36:06.372 --> 36:07.732
Again?

36:07.732 --> 36:10.152
I have an iron flute of south

36:10.652 --> 36:13.252
that wants to lean
on a fragrant, snowy twig.

36:13.252 --> 36:16.111
Blowing through the jade dawn,

36:17.372 --> 36:19.531
its clear shadow is hard to catch...

36:19.531 --> 36:20.451
This one is also acceptable.

36:20.451 --> 36:23.312
...in the fluff flying across the sky.

36:24.491 --> 36:26.971
Drifting away, I and you...

36:26.971 --> 36:29.172
I think the last two versions
are both good.

36:29.172 --> 36:31.392
...paddle on the cloud.

36:31.971 --> 36:33.951
I prefer the second one.

36:34.652 --> 36:35.712
Sheng.

36:36.892 --> 36:38.312
Which one do you prefer?

36:47.732 --> 36:50.991
I like them both. They are both good.

36:53.212 --> 36:54.392
Can't make a choice?

36:55.571 --> 36:56.951
No, I can't.

36:57.611 --> 36:59.611
Basically, to young girls,

36:59.611 --> 37:01.812
100 versions of you are equally good.

37:01.812 --> 37:06.392
Don't you have confidence
in your own voice?

37:09.131 --> 37:11.312
Then let me think about it again.

37:12.292 --> 37:14.131
Mao, play it two more times.

37:14.131 --> 37:16.071
Two more times? Alright.

37:17.611 --> 37:20.332
I have an iron flute of south

37:20.332 --> 37:23.011
that wants to lean
on a fragrant, snowy twig.

37:23.011 --> 37:25.172
Blowing through the jade dawn,

37:25.172 --> 37:26.812
its clear shadow is hard to catch...

37:26.812 --> 37:28.732
Shengshengman, isn't it strange?

37:28.732 --> 37:30.091
...in the fluff flying across the sky.

37:30.091 --> 37:31.836
I mean the way he eats.

37:32.531 --> 37:35.411
Drifting away, I and you

37:35.411 --> 37:37.131
paddle on the cloud.

37:37.131 --> 37:40.051
He really cherishes
his thumb and index finger.

37:40.051 --> 37:43.260
Because of work, he has eaten chips
like this since he was in school.

37:44.812 --> 37:45.852
She believed?

37:45.852 --> 37:46.931
Just kidding.

37:46.931 --> 37:50.236
We've said it one hundred times
and he still won't change his bad habit.

37:52.652 --> 37:54.431
I can do this too. I'll show you.

37:54.971 --> 37:56.172
Seriously?

37:56.172 --> 37:57.471
Hold it like this.

37:59.332 --> 38:02.131
Never mind.
Let's think about what to eat tonight.

38:02.131 --> 38:04.732
Leave this part
for the post-production period.

38:04.732 --> 38:06.652
Leaving it to post-production
means leaving it to me, right?

38:06.652 --> 38:09.276
Great. I'm already hungry.

38:09.852 --> 38:11.051
Oh no, I'm hungry too.

38:11.051 --> 38:12.011
Wait a bit.

38:12.011 --> 38:13.011
Just wait a moment.

38:13.011 --> 38:14.692
Let's sit for a while.

38:14.692 --> 38:15.372
Sit for a while.

38:15.372 --> 38:16.332
What's going on?

38:16.332 --> 38:17.352
Come on.

38:17.971 --> 38:19.372
I have a proposal.

38:19.372 --> 38:23.411
How about we have some memento
before we leave?

38:23.411 --> 38:25.692
What kind of memento?
You must be up to no good.

38:25.692 --> 38:29.091
Look, Sheng loves
Mr. Mo's voice the most.

38:29.091 --> 38:30.491
We can all see that.

38:30.491 --> 38:33.411
Mr. Mo also said that
he loves Sheng's voice the most.

38:33.411 --> 38:35.372
Now that we're here
in the recording studio,

38:35.372 --> 38:39.011
why not take this rare opportunity
to record a few more songs as a memento?

38:39.011 --> 38:42.844
In my opinion,
since you love each other so much

38:44.772 --> 38:45.951
in terms of voice,

38:46.652 --> 38:49.111
why not collaborate on a song right now?

38:49.652 --> 38:50.372
How about that?

38:50.372 --> 38:51.852
It's not a bad idea.

38:51.852 --> 38:52.692
I agree.

38:52.692 --> 38:53.991
I second that.

38:56.252 --> 38:57.591
That sounds good.

38:58.531 --> 39:00.832
Come on. Mr. Mo, you understand me.

39:01.892 --> 39:05.172
Consider it a Valentine's Day gift
for the fans.

39:05.172 --> 39:06.892
Yes, it's almost Valentine's Day.

39:06.892 --> 39:08.292
It's right after the New Year.

39:08.292 --> 39:10.712
Good days just keep coming.

39:13.091 --> 39:14.551
How about

39:16.772 --> 39:19.431
Return with You?

39:20.971 --> 39:22.511
This song...

39:23.252 --> 39:25.091
I thought
it was only their second meeting.

39:25.091 --> 39:26.332
Return with You already?

39:26.332 --> 39:28.131
That's too high-profile.

39:28.131 --> 39:30.411
He's never been in a relationship.
He wants to skip straight to the end.

39:30.411 --> 39:33.312
He's being overly anxious.

39:36.571 --> 39:38.792
You two go on.

39:40.931 --> 39:44.131
I don't sing very often.
I'm familiar with this one only.

39:44.131 --> 39:46.832
I'm also quite familiar with it.

39:48.091 --> 39:50.611
Is this song composed by you?

39:50.611 --> 39:51.411
Yes.

39:51.411 --> 39:53.091
This song is quite popular, isn't it?

39:53.091 --> 39:54.491
I remember since I was young...

39:54.491 --> 39:55.411
You...

39:55.411 --> 39:57.571
No, I've really listened to it
many times.

39:57.571 --> 40:00.172
In the past, when I listened to it,
I only noticed who sang it.

40:00.172 --> 40:02.111
I didn't pay attention
to the composition.

40:03.451 --> 40:04.672
Then let's sing it.

40:06.332 --> 40:07.792
Okay.

40:17.652 --> 40:19.011
You use this.

40:19.011 --> 40:20.392
Okay, thank you.

40:20.931 --> 40:22.591
Come closer. Let me see the height.

40:27.332 --> 40:29.332
Here, the lyrics.

40:29.332 --> 40:30.872
Thank you.

40:33.971 --> 40:35.392
Look at him.

40:40.772 --> 40:42.991
Do you need to review the lyrics?

40:45.091 --> 40:46.931
I'm not very familiar with the lyrics.

40:46.931 --> 40:50.491
I might need to practice
with the instrumental version once.

40:50.491 --> 40:52.471
How do you want to perform the duet?

40:53.491 --> 40:54.991
The key is quite high.

40:56.091 --> 40:59.531
I think you should sing part A1.

40:59.531 --> 41:01.416
(Return with You)
And then I'll sing part A2.

41:01.416 --> 41:04.951
In section B, we take turns.

41:07.571 --> 41:11.511
As for chorus,
we harmonize with each other.

41:12.131 --> 41:13.692
In fact, I haven't figured it out yet.

41:13.692 --> 41:17.692
Why don't we feel it first
with the accompaniment?

41:17.692 --> 41:21.951
Okay. This song is quite high-pitched.

41:23.051 --> 41:26.392
When I wrote it, I thought
it was more suitable for a female voice.

41:27.011 --> 41:28.792
Can you handle the chorus?

41:30.172 --> 41:31.192
No problem.

41:33.931 --> 41:35.692
He's totally ignoring us.

41:35.692 --> 41:37.192
How considerate.

41:37.892 --> 41:40.131
How's it? Ready? Let's get started.

41:40.131 --> 41:41.692
No, Mao.

41:42.372 --> 41:45.312
We need to familiarize ourselves
with the lyrics. Play the accompaniment.

41:46.051 --> 41:47.312
Okay.

42:03.611 --> 42:05.431
I'm ready, Mr. Qiang Qingci.

42:07.571 --> 42:11.420
You can call me Qiang Qingci
or Mo Qingcheng.

42:12.011 --> 42:13.611
You don't need to call me "Mr".

42:13.611 --> 42:17.631
You can call him Qingcheng or Qingci.

42:18.451 --> 42:20.812
Sheng, call him Mo Qingcheng.

42:20.812 --> 42:22.252
Qiang Qingci sounds a little unfamiliar.

42:22.252 --> 42:24.444
I agree. Mo Qingcheng is fine.

42:25.000 --> 42:27.491
If you want to become friends
in real life,

42:27.491 --> 42:29.832
it's better to call him Mo Qingcheng.

42:30.892 --> 42:32.692
It doesn't matter.

42:32.692 --> 42:34.551
I just don't want you
to feel constrained.

42:39.212 --> 42:41.232
Mo Qingcheng.

42:41.772 --> 42:44.571
See? It sounds much better.

42:44.571 --> 42:46.051
Can I call you that?

42:46.051 --> 42:47.792
Of course.

42:48.812 --> 42:50.031
Are you ready?

42:50.892 --> 42:53.991
Let's find the right feeling first,
then officially start recording.

42:55.411 --> 42:57.111
Keep the energy for the end.

42:58.252 --> 42:59.591
Mao.

43:00.732 --> 43:01.652
Yes?

43:01.652 --> 43:05.096
Let's start from section B.

43:05.096 --> 43:05.692
Okay.

43:05.692 --> 43:06.491
Section B.

43:06.491 --> 43:07.011
Okay.

43:07.011 --> 43:08.931
